<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Social Connections - Learning Experience</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #3B82A0;
            --primary-light: #E8F4F8;
            --accent: #7BAE94;
            --accent-light: #E8F3EE;
            --bg-white: #FFFFFF;
            --bg-light: #F7FAFB;
            --text-dark: #1E3A4F;
            --text-light: #6B8499;
            --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(30, 58, 79, 0.06);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 20px rgba(30, 58, 79, 0.1);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F7FB 0%, #F7FAFB 100%);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .app-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F7FB 0%, #F7FAFB 100%);
        }

        .phone-frame {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 375px;
            height: 812px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 40px;
            border: 12px solid #000;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
        }

        .phone-frame::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 150px;
            height: 28px;
            background: #000;
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .screen-content {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            padding-top: 12px;
        }

        .screen {
            display: none;
            flex: 1;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-in-out;
        }

        .screen.active {
            display: flex;
            opacity: 1;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* Status Bar */
        .status-bar {
            height: 36px;
            background: var(--bg-white);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 79, 0.08);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
        }

        .status-bar-left, .status-bar-right {
            display: flex;
            gap: 4px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* Bottom Navigation */
        .bottom-nav {
            height: 60px;
            background: var(--bg-white);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 79, 0.08);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
        }

        .nav-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--text-light);
            transition: color 0.3s;
            font-size: 11px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .nav-item.active {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .nav-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* Screen Content */
        .screen-body {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .centered-intro {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            flex: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .centered-intro h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .centered-intro p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Welcome Screen */
        .welcome-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .welcome-header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .welcome-header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .carousel {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .carousel-slide {
            display: none;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s;
        }

        .carousel-slide.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .carousel-slide h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .carousel-slide p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .carousel-dots {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #DDD;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .dot.active {
            background: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn {
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .screen > .btn-primary {
            margin: 12px 20px 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #2E6B85;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #E8EDF2;
        }

        /* Cards */
        .card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .card-desc {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Survey */
        .survey-question {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .survey-question-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .likert-scale {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .likert-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px 6px;
            border: 2px solid #DDD;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .likert-btn:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .likert-btn.selected {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Progress Bar */
        .progress-container {
            padding: 16px 20px;
            background: var(--bg-white);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 79, 0.08);
        }

        .progress-bar {
            height: 4px;
            background: #E8EDF2;
            border-radius: 2px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--primary);
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }

        .progress-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Section Cards Grid */
        .section-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .section-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .section-card-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .section-card-title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .badge {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }

        .badge-available {
            background: var(--primary-light);
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .badge-completed {
            background: var(--accent-light);
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .badge-locked {
            background: #E8EDF2;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Chips */
        .chip-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 12px 0;
        }

        .chip {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: 2px solid #DDD;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 13px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .chip:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .chip.selected {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Chat */
        .chat-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .chat-bubble {
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            max-width: 85%;
        }

        .chat-ai {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            align-self: flex-start;
        }

        .chat-user {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            align-self: flex-end;
        }

        .chat-input {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 0 20px 12px;
        }

        .chat-input input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border: 2px solid #DDD;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
        }

        .chat-input button {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        /* Contact Cards */
        .contact-card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .contact-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .contact-avatar {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--primary-light);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .contact-info {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .contact-name {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .contact-role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .contact-checkbox {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border: 2px solid #DDD;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .contact-card.selected .contact-checkbox {
            background: var(--primary);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Sticky Notes */
        .sticky-notes {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .sticky-note {
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            min-height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .sticky-blue {
            background: #E8F4F8;
            color: #3B82A0;
        }

        .sticky-green {
            background: #E8F3EE;
            color: #7BAE94;
        }

        .sticky-cream {
            background: #FEF9F0;
            color: #C4956F;
        }

        /* Belief Cards */
        .belief-card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .belief-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .belief-card.selected {
            background: var(--primary-light);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .belief-card-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Slider */
        .slider-container {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .slider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            background: #DDD;
            outline: none;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            appearance: none;
        }

        .slider::-webkit-slider-thumb {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            appearance: none;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .slider::-moz-range-thumb {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary);
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }

        .slider-labels {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* Decorative Swoop */
        .swoop {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInStory {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Chart */
        .bar-chart {
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .chart-bar {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .chart-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .chart-bar-container {
            height: 24px;
            background: #E8EDF2;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .chart-bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }

        /* Hub Screen */
        .hub-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hub-header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .hub-header p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Pathway Cards */
        .pathway-cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .pathway-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light) 0%, rgba(123, 174, 148, 0.1) 100%);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .pathway-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .pathway-card h3 {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .pathway-card p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Activity Previews */
        .activity-preview {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .activity-preview-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .activity-preview-desc {
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        /* Results */
        .results-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .results-card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .results-card h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        /* Responsive Desktop */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .app-container {
                justify-content: center;
                padding: 40px 20px;
            }

            .phone-frame {
                box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            }
        }

        /* Scrollbar Styling */
        .screen-content::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }

        .screen-content::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: transparent;
        }

        .screen-content::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: rgba(30, 58, 79, 0.2);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .screen-content::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: rgba(30, 58, 79, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <svg style="position:absolute;width:0;height:0">
        <defs>
            <linearGradient id="swoopGrad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#3B82A0;stop-opacity:1"/>
                <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#7BAE94;stop-opacity:1"/>
            </linearGradient>
        </defs>
    </svg>
    <div class="app-container">
        <div class="phone-frame">
            <div class="status-bar">
                <div class="status-bar-left">
                    <span>9:41</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-bar-right">
                    <svg width="16" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 12" fill="var(--text-dark)"><rect x="0" y="8" width="3" height="4" rx="0.5"/><rect x="4" y="5" width="3" height="7" rx="0.5"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="3" height="10" rx="0.5"/><rect x="12" y="0" width="3" height="12" rx="0.5"/></svg>
                    <svg width="24" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 12" fill="var(--text-dark)"><rect x="0" y="1" width="20" height="10" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><rect x="2" y="3" width="14" height="6" rx="1" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="21" y="3.5" width="2" height="5" rx="1" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="screen-content" id="screenContent">
                <!-- Screen 1: Welcome -->
                <div class="screen active" id="screen-welcome">
                    <div class="screen-body">
                        <div class="welcome-header">
                            <h1>Social<br>Connections</h1>
                            <p>Building the connections that move you forward</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="carousel">
                            <div class="carousel-slide active">
                                <h2>This isn't a course</h2>
                                <p>It's a set of experiences designed to help you notice, understand, and use the connections around you.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-slide">
                                <h2>Go at your own pace</h2>
                                <p>Every activity is built for your phone. Nothing takes more than a few minutes.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-slide">
                                <h2>Start where it feels right</h2>
                                <p>You'll start with a quick check-in about how you see networking. Then you'll choose your own path.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="carousel-dots">
                            <div class="dot active" onclick="goToCarouselSlide(0)"></div>
                            <div class="dot" onclick="goToCarouselSlide(1)"></div>
                            <div class="dot" onclick="goToCarouselSlide(2)"></div>
                        </div>

                        <svg class="swoop" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M200 200 C200 120, 160 80, 80 80 C40 80, 10 100, 0 140 L0 200 Z" fill="url(#swoopGrad)" opacity="0.12"/>
                            <path d="M200 200 C200 150, 170 110, 110 110 C70 110, 40 130, 20 160 L20 200 Z" fill="url(#swoopGrad)" opacity="0.08"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>

                    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="goToScreen('survey')">Get Started</button>
                </div>

                <!-- Screen 2: Survey -->
                <div class="screen" id="screen-survey">
                    <div class="progress-container">
                        <div class="progress-bar">
                            <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 15%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-text">1 of 5</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="screen-body">
                        <h2 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--text-dark);">Before we start, let's see where you are</h2>
                        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 20px;">How much do you agree with each statement?</p>

                        <div class="survey-question">
                            <div class="survey-question-text">Networking is something you're either good at or you're not</div>
